---
import { BookOpen, Globe, UserRound } from "@lucide/astro";

const socialLinks = [
  { href: "https://github.com/akisysama", label: "GitHub", icon: Globe, external: true },
  { href: "/about/", label: "关于", icon: UserRound },
  { href: "/posts/", label: "文章", icon: BookOpen },
];
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-intro">
    <p class="footer-title">保持联系</p>
    <p>欢迎交换想法，也欢迎分享你正在做的有趣事情。</p>
    <a class="text-link" href="/about/">关于我 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-links">
    <p class="footer-title">快速导航</p>
    <a href="/">首页</a>
    <a href="/posts/">文章</a>
    <a href="/tags/">标签</a>
    <a href="/about/">关于</a>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-follow">
    <p class="footer-title">关注</p>
    <nav class="footer-social" aria-label="页脚链接">
      {
        socialLinks.map(({ href, label, icon: Icon, external }) => (
          <a
            href={href}
            aria-label={label}
            title={label}
            target={external ? "_blank" : undefined}
            rel={external ? "noreferrer" : undefined}
          >
            <Icon class="icon-muted" size={17} stroke-width={1.5} />
          </a>
        ))
      }
    </nav>
  </div>
  <blockquote>
    “原本想做个高雅的网站，最后发现我高雅不起来”
  </blockquote>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Akisy. All rights reserved.</span>
    <span>Built with Astro · Love & Peace</span>
  </div>
</footer>
